## Summary (informational, not a substitute for the full license)

### Regular License
- One End Product (one website / one organization)
- End users may interact with the product without restriction
- Source code modification permitted
- Distribution of the product as-is or compiled is NOT permitted
- One purchased Envato license = one deployment

### Extended License
- Same as Regular, but End Users may pay a fee to access the End Product
  (i.e., commercial SaaS / subscription deployment)

